piaware-ble-connect (7.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * First release of Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) service for PiAware
  * Implements a UART service to handle requests from FlightAware BLE central
    applications to configure PiAware WiFi over Bluetooth LE

